articles.author: Hilary Whiteman
articles.title: Tech companies put on notice as Australia passes world-first social media ban for under-16s - CNN
articles.description: Australia’s parliament has passed a law banning social media for children under 16, putting tech companies on notice to tighten security before a cut-off date that’s yet to be set.
